All Known Implementing Classes:
SimpleMappedRegistry
public interface MappedRegistry<KEY,VALUE,MAPPING extends Map<KEY,VALUE>> extends Registry<MAPPING>
An abstract registry holding a map of various registrations as defined by MappedRegistry. The M represents the map class, which can be anything that extends Map. The MappedRegistry and MappedRegistry generics are the key and value respectively.
